values:
Hey.....I havent been on here in like a month...so there is a lot to catch up on. I am threw with Megan....yeah. Now I am with this magnificant girl named Ari. She is my hott sexy love. I love skateboarding.... Whats new?....haha.
I am sitting here waiting for youth group...I love it there it is great. Well....I am going to get going...Later everyone...Love ya Ari.

Hello everyone. Wow I just found out that Paul Rodriguez ( the greatest skate ever alive ) is sponsered by Nike! But oh well this is Paul Rodriguez we are talking about. I am getting his shoes once they come out. Even if they are Nike. Well....I had KFC for dinner. I got popcorn chicken. Yummy. Haha. I called my love Megan today. For some reason I feel she is angry or upset with me. I hope not. Well I am buying Royal trucks. The reason is P - Rod rides for them! I wish to meet him someday. Skate with him and shit. That would be great. I wish it would never snow again. I hate it. Cant skate or anything. Curse the fucking snow! I Wanna live in Cali. or Florida. Thats my goal before I turn 20. I am gonna take a road trip to Cali and on the way tried to get sponsered. Everyone think I am not gonna be skateing anymore by 18 but I will not matter what. I will skate until I cant walk. Haha.... Anyone wanna email me can at mattdeckelman@hotmail.com if you want. Well I am gonna get going. Later everyone. Skate forever.

Well....here it is 7:53 PM and I am exhausted. Well today after I at breakfast and got on here me and my mom went to eat at The Famous Hot Weiner. It was alrite. Then I went to the mall and got a Bootleg shirt. Bored as hell I came home and went to Cody's. We pretty much just hung out. Then we went to his neighbors house and played pool. I won a few times. I had fun. I didn't get to skate. Bummer. Well now I am gonna get going and try to call the love of my life Megan. Later.

Hello. Good morning.... I just woke up and got on here. Then I got breakfast. Nothing very exciting happened yet. Haha. Hell yeah no school....just a good thing to start off the day.I will probably go down Cody's later. Skate the day away. I talked to the girl I admire this morning. But I had to get off the phone. The girl I admire is Megan Smith. I love her. We started going out 1 - 13 - 04. I have never been happier ever since. I hope we last. I have nothing else really to say about this morning. Later.
